					>
						<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">1</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">Scan & Discover</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300">
						Cogency automatically scans your tools/ directory for Python files
						containing tool classes at startup.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="text-center">
					<div
						class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-500/10"
					>
						<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">2</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-white">Load & Register</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300">
						Found tools are dynamically imported, instantiated, and registered
